OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778324573
OL,3,CNorth West MPs call on Starmer to go
OL,4,Cafter 'catastrophic' local elections
OL,6,FNorth West Labour MPs have called on
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer to
OL,8,Fquit or set a timetable for his
OL,9,Fdeparture from Number 10.
OL,11,FIt's after a disastrous showing in the
OL,12,Flocal elections which saw the party
OL,13,Flose hundreds of councillors, mainly
OL,14,Fto Reform UK, led by Nigel Farage.
OL,16,FReform are celebrating a stunning
OL,17,Fvictory in St Helens where they took
OL,18,Fcontrol of the council by winning 34
OL,19,Fof its 48 seats.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778324573
OL,3,CNorth West MPs call on Starmer to go
OL,4,Cafter 'catastrophic' local elections
OL,6,FLabour were virtually wiped out and
OL,7,Fthe results being described as
OL,8,F"seismic" and "unprecedented".
OL,10,FThere were also significant gains for
OL,11,Fthe Greens, who were the big winners
OL,12,Fin Manchester City Council.
OL,14,FThey gained 17 new seats, meaning they
OL,15,Fnow have 21 of the 96 seats.
OL,17,FLabour MP for Liverpool West Derby,
OL,18,FIan Byrne, said: "Across towns and
OL,19,Fcities that should be Labour
OL,20,Fheartlands, our base has collapsed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778324573
OL,3,CNorth West MPs call on Starmer to go
OL,4,Cafter 'catastrophic' local elections
OL,6,F"We cannot brush this off as a bad
OL,7,Fnight or a messaging issue. This is a
OL,8,Fpolitical crisis for the entire Labour
OL,9,Fmovement.
OL,11,F"How we respond now will determine
OL,12,Fwhether the Labour Party remains a
OL,13,Frelevant political force for years,
OL,14,Fand decades, to come.
OL,16,F"The Prime Minister has reached the
OL,17,Fpoint where the question is no longer
OL,18,Fwhether he can recover, but whether
OL,19,Fstaying on causes lasting damage to
OL,20,FLabour's ability to rebuild trust and
OL,21,Fstop the advance of the right."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778324573
OL,3,CNorth West MPs call on Starmer to go
OL,4,Cafter 'catastrophic' local elections
OL,6,F"The longer this drags on, the greater
OL,7,Fthe damage to the party and the
OL,8,Fcountry.
OL,10,F"The Prime Minister must now set out a
OL,11,Fclear timetable for his departure, and
OL,12,Frestore our party's democratic
OL,13,Fprocesses for selecting candidates,
OL,14,Fwhich have been shamefully eroded in
OL,15,Frecent years."
OL,17,FMr Starmer said he took responsibility
OL,18,Ffor the "tough" results, but insisted
OL,19,Fhe would carry on as prime minister.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
