PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778324573
OL,3,CNorth West MPs call on Starmer to go
OL,4,Cafter 'catastrophic' local elections
OL,6,FCrewe and Nantwich MP Connor Naismith
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is clear to me that we need
OL,8,Fnew leadership" and called for Andy
OL,9,FBurnham to be given the opportunity to
OL,10,F"re-enter parliament if an opportunity
OL,11,Farises and if he wishes to do so".
OL,13,FMr Burnham, the Mayor of Greater
OL,14,FManchester, is being widely touted as
OL,15,Fa candidate to replace Mr Starmer as
OL,16,FLabour leader and Prime Minister.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778324573
OL,3,CNorth West MPs call on Starmer to go
OL,4,Cafter 'catastrophic' local elections
OL,6,FConnor Naismith said: "In the wake of
OL,7,Fthese catastrophic local elections
OL,8,Fresults, with regret, it is clear to
OL,9,Fme that we need new leadership.
OL,10,FLeadership which is capable of
OL,11,Fbringing together a broad coalition of
OL,12,Fvoters to stop the Thatcherite
OL,13,Fpolitics of Reform UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778324573
OL,3,CNorth West MPs call on Starmer to go
OL,4,Cafter 'catastrophic' local elections
OL,6,F"The world is in a turbulent place so
OL,7,Fany transition of power should be
OL,8,Forderly, and should facilitate voices
OL,9,Ffrom across our movement to chart the
OL,10,Fcourse for what we do next. That must
OL,11,Finclude giving Andy Burnham the
OL,12,Fopportunity to re-enter parliament if
OL,13,Fan opportunity arises and if he wishes
OL,14,Fto do so."
OL,16,FSome MPs have also come out to say
OL,17,Fthat a change at the top is the last
OL,18,Fthing the country needs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778324573
OL,3,CNorth West MPs call on Starmer to go
OL,4,Cafter 'catastrophic' local elections
OL,6,FBury North MP James Frith said the
OL,7,Fparty "won't deliver for our
OL,8,Fcommunities or serve the national
OL,9,Finterest by turning in on ourselves".
OL,11,FHe added: "We must dust ourselves off,
OL,12,Fcome together and get back to
OL,13,Fdelivering for the people who elected
OL,14,Fus with a landslide just two years ago.
OL,16,F"The PM is right not to walk away or
OL,17,Ftalking timetables. At a moment like
OL,18,Fthis, the country needs focus,
OL,19,Fstability and delivery, not chaos."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
