OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778324573
OL,3,CNorth West MPs call on Starmer to go
OL,4,Cafter 'catastrophic' local elections
OL,6,FAnd Deputy Leader Lucy Powell, who is
OL,7,FMP for Manchester Central, told the
OL,8,FBBC the party needs to change its
OL,9,Fapproach but stick with Starmer.
OL,11,F"Yes, yes, yes," she said when asked
OL,12,Fif Starmer will still be leader in six
OL,13,Fmonths' time.
OL,15,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,16,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,17,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,18,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
